#: Site-Behavior-Auditor.php:1187
msgid "📖 使用说明"
msgstr "📖 Instructions"

#: Site-Behavior-Auditor.php:1188
msgid "1. <b>防误杀：</b> 填入用户名后，登录时将免疫所有频率拦截和路径检测。"
msgstr "1. <b>Whitelist Users:</b> Users listed here will bypass all rate limits and path checks."

#: Site-Behavior-Auditor.php:1189
msgid "2. <b>Gate 钥匙：</b> 设置后，访问 <code>wp-login.php?gate=钥匙</code> 可开启登录入口（地址栏自动去除参数）。此后登录表单通过隐藏字段提交令牌，退出后令牌失效。"
msgstr "2. <b>Gate Key:</b> Set a secret key. Access <code>wp-login.php?gate=your-key</code> to enable the login page (the parameter will be removed). The login form will then submit a token via hidden field, which expires after logout."

#: Site-Behavior-Auditor.php:1190
msgid "3. <b>指纹库：</b> 自动识别 <code>sqlmap, curl, wget, python</code> 等 UA 特征并阻断。"
msgstr "3. <b>Fingerprinting:</b> Automatically detects and blocks common scanner UA strings like <code>sqlmap, curl, wget, python</code>."

#: Site-Behavior-Auditor.php:1191
msgid "4. <b>归属地：</b> 使用 ip2region xdb 内存查询。请通过下方按钮上传 IPv4 和 IPv6 的 xdb 文件（支持分片上传、断点续传）。"
msgstr "4. <b>GeoIP:</b> Uses ip2region xdb in-memory query. Upload IPv4 and IPv6 xdb files using the buttons below (chunked upload with resume support)."

#: Site-Behavior-Auditor.php:1192
msgid "5. <b>爬虫防御：</b> 启用阶梯限制和 Cookie 校验可有效识别采集器，蜜罐陷阱触发即封禁。"
msgstr "5. <b>Anti-Scraping:</b> Enabling tiered rate limits and cookie validation effectively detects scrapers; honeypot traps will trigger an immediate ban."

